>>>>>>Step to create package.json<<<<<<<<<<<
*NodeJs must be installed in the system
> navigate to the folder using cmd/terminal
> type npm init
> answer all questions
> type yes


///////
Step to intall packages
///////
> navigate to the folder using cmd
> npm i react

//////////////////////
Step to generate react application
////////////////////////
//window
>>>Only One Time in one system<<<
> open cmd as admin
> npm i -g create-react-app

>>>>Net Every Time when i Need New App<<<<
> go inside the the folder where you want to generate app
> create-react-app applicationname

//Mac
>>>Only One Time in one system<<<
> open terminal
> sudo npm i -g create-react-app

>>>>Net Every Time when i Need New App<<<<
> go inside the the folder where you want to generate app
> create-react-app applicationname


http://localhost:3000/

react > main lib for application
react-dom > this help to render the app
react-script > this help to run the application

component based
//////////////////
Class Component
> logical component
> We call api and manage state
> state can be defined
> heavy as compare to functional

Functional
> Dumb Component
> Use for display purpose
> state cannot be defined
> Light in weigth

Hooks


state
props
class

State > Act like a local variable
> scope is inside one component
> Any data interaction will happen through state
> state value can be updated

Props > Props help to transfer data/state
> value of props cannot be updated
> we can use props in both clas and function component

                 Props
component A      ======>     Component B
State="data"                 state=""


Data can be pass from one component to another if it is nested 

everytime state will update component will rerender


map
filter 
indexof

parent => child (props) 
child => parent( props with function)


